AMPScript Language Module for BBEdit v1.2 and TextWrangler, (2011/08/16)
----------------------------------------------------

The AMPScript Language Module introduces syntax colorization for the AMPScript programming language to BBEdit 9.0/TextWrangler and higher.



Installation
------------

Put it manually into "~/Library/Application Support/TextWrangler/Language Modules/".


Source code is available on Google Code:
https://github.com/fancentric/AMPScript-Language-Module

Current limitations
-------------------

* Highlights current AMPScript functions and reserved keywords



Change history
--------------

1.0 (2011/08/15).
        Initial build.


